      These enables us to recognize your previously selected preferences, which includes, language, location, nutrition types, e.t.c. 
      For more information visit Privacy Policy.
  </h5>
      </div>
      <div class="cookiesButtons">
        <button  type="button" class="allowAllCookies" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"  > 
            <h6> Deny all</h6>
          </button>
  
        <button  type="button" class="denyAll"   data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"  >
          <h6> Allow all cookies</h6>
  
        </button>
        
    </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
 

